snippet.textDisplay:
This is a scam, and they are only sending units to reviewers. The reason I believe this is Pablo Phone LTD is a UK based company which gives the company a separate legal identity. A separate legal identity means the company is separate from its directors, which in this case is Pablo Escobar's Brother (Roberto Escobar Gaviria). This means if any legal action is taken against this company, it will only be taken against the company itself and not its directors. Not to mention the fact that they only take direct deposits and crypto currency now which makes it so you can't get a refund. Sources for anyone interested:

https://www.fraudadvisorypanel.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Abuse-of-Incorporation-November-2012.pdf

https://www.escobarinc.com/product/fold2/ (Bottom of the Escobar Inc site has a disclaimer saying Pablo Phones LTD is responsible for the loss of property and/or any losses caused by the use of this device)
